Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra. This is Olivia speaking.

Speaker 2: Who do I have the pleasure of speaking with today?

Speaker 1: Michael Kaniglia.

Speaker 2: trying to get through to you.

Speaker 1: Yes, well it is Monday morning and we opened one hour ago.

Speaker 2: So that is probably why. Hello Michael.

Speaker 2: It should be able to be done online. This is ridiculous.

Speaker 1: Yes, I can definitely help you with that. What is your date of birth?

Speaker 2: 10-11-65.

Speaker 1: Great. And you are located in Omaha, Nebraska?

Speaker 2: Correct.

Speaker 1: Yes, so if you don't want to receive those regular refills with your prescription

Speaker 2: you certainly don't have to. You always have the option to place

Speaker 1: your prescription on hold for up to 6 months at a time just because 6 months

Speaker 2: is when the prescription would expire. If we didn't refill it

Speaker 1: and the way that would work if you did want to place it on hold today

Speaker 2: is that you could order over the next 6 months or before July 27th.

Speaker 1: You just have to give us a call to place the order yourself whenever you are.

Speaker 2: To be honest, I'm never going to reorder from you.

Speaker 1: Customer service is not good and this stuff doesn't work anyway,

Speaker 2: so it's no different than a regular Viagra pill.

Speaker 1: Okay. So the pills, they didn't work for you?

Speaker 2: No.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: And I didn't know I was getting automatic refills until I saw it on my credit card

Speaker 1: and then I got them. So I'm not trying to send them back or anything.

Speaker 2: I just want to stop it.

Speaker 1: Okay. Okay. Well, that makes sense.

Speaker 2: Just so you know, it is part of my job to let you know,

Speaker 1: if the pills don't work for you, it looks like you are qualified to try a free sample.

Speaker 2: It would be 10 pills of our newest, highest quality products,

Speaker 1: which is a superior prescription to yours.

Speaker 2: They are our fastest acting, longest lasting stuff.

Speaker 1: They're FDA approved, third party tested, all that good stuff.

Speaker 2: But my favorite thing about them specifically is they've been formulated to cut out

Speaker 1: the side effects of sinus agitation and headache.

Speaker 2: And they come with basically like a five month free trial

Speaker 1: where if I were to start that prescription for you with a free sample of 10 pills,

Speaker 2: I could place it on hold for you until June while you try it out,

Speaker 1: make sure you love it, make sure you prefer it to your old script.

Speaker 2: We believe you would, and obviously the old script is canceled

Speaker 1: because they don't work for you, so you don't need them.

Speaker 2: But what we believe would happen based off of the data is that you'd give us a call back

Speaker 1: in two to five months to order some, and then we might be able to keep you,

Speaker 2: and that would make it worth it to us.

Speaker 1: Well, I'm willing to try that, and I appreciate it, and I'm willing to try that,

Speaker 2: as long as I don't pay anything and I don't get automatic refills.

Speaker 1: You know, I just don't want to – I don't even know, honestly,

Speaker 2: I don't know how many I would use because, you know,

Speaker 1: there's not that many times we do things, so, you know.

Speaker 2: Yeah, no, that's fine. Okay.

Speaker 1: What is the new one, just so I know? I mean, I'm happy to try it,

Speaker 2: and I appreciate it very much.

Speaker 1: Yeah, of course. So it is a new Viagra. It comes from our Pfizer labs in France,

Speaker 2: and it's – yeah, it's the best stuff we have on the market.

Speaker 1: So isn't that what I got, the AGV? Isn't that the same thing?

Speaker 2: No. You were receiving our American stuff, and this is our French stuff, so.

Speaker 1: Okay. Well, I'm willing to try it. I've never been with a French woman, so let's try it.

Speaker 2: Why not? Yeah, yeah, yeah. Okay.

Speaker 1: So, yeah, this is going to be 10 pills, 100 milligrams.

Speaker 2: Can I ship them – and the sample is completely free, I want to be really clear –

Speaker 1: to 5634 North 142nd Avenue, Omaha, Nebraska, 68164?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Okay, great. And you said you guys don't use them super often,

Speaker 2: so I can give you – I can do until July. So just let us know by July, either way.

Speaker 1: That's going to be a Wednesday, July 1st. But I think you're going to love them.

Speaker 2: And as long as you take them on an empty stomach, that's really important.

Speaker 1: And then you want to avoid alcohol and caffeine the day you take them.

Speaker 2: It's not as much a safety issue. It's more just an efficacy

Speaker 1: and, like, success with the pill issue.

Speaker 2: Where caffeine and alcohol restrict blood flow, and you want more, not less.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: So, yeah, I hope you enjoy these.

Speaker 1: And we're always here Monday through Friday, 8 to 5 Pacific, at this phone number.

Speaker 2: Well, I really appreciate it.

Speaker 1: And I did submit a secondary ticket while I was on hold to say just cancel my account,

Speaker 2: but I'm sure they'll see what you did and they'll leave it alone.

Speaker 1: Okay, cool. Great. Well, I hope you love these, and I think you will.

Speaker 2: Well, I appreciate your help. Thank you.

Speaker 1: Yeah, of course. I hope you have a good day.

Speaker 2: Have a good day. Bye.

Speaker 1: Yeah.
